name: Friday Night Funkin' Scary Swings (HTML5)
description:
To play Scary Swings:

Load up week 2 in story mode on normal or hard (not on easy)

or 

In freeplay, load up Spookeez on normal or hard (still not on easy)

Attempting to load up Spookeez or easy will crash the game.
